The '''YVH S-series war droid''' was the space assault model of the [[YVH-Series battle droid]] produced by [[Tendrando Arms]]. [[YVH 2-1S]] and [[YVH 2-4S]] were two S-series war droids that were sent on the [[Mission to Myrkr]], and by [[45 ABY]], Tendrando Arms had developed the [[YVH-8 S-series battle droid]].

